  "title": "Senior Marketing Executive (EdTech) - Up to 4K #HHL",
  "description": "<p>Salary: Up to 4K<br />Location: Paya lebar <br /><br /><strong>Key Duties</strong><br />• Plan and run marketing campaigns<br />• Create content for social media, emails, and promotions<br />• Manage social media platforms (IG, FB, TikTok, WeChat, Xiao Hong Shu)<br />• Handle customer enquiries on social channels<br />• Support events, exhibitions, and offline marketing<br />• Track and report campaign performance<br />• Assist with ad-hoc admin tasks</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong><br />• Min Degree<br />• Strong communication skills<br />• Business-minded, able to generate leads<br />• Good eye for branding and design<br />• Basic video editing skills<br />• Proactive, organised, and fast learner<br /></p><p>If interested, please email me at alexgoh@recruitexpress.com.sg or telegram @alexgohhl</p><p>➖</p><p>Alex Goh Hock Leong</p><p>(CEI.No: R1763413 l Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Life Science) | 99C4599)</p>",
